      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "import torch\n",
        "from torchvision import transforms\n",
        "from PIL import Image\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "0XM5aPDRRRbP"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "input_folder = \"/content/pictures\"  # 存放拍摄图像的文件夹\n",
        "output_folder = \"/content/grey_pictures\"    # 存放处理后图像的文件夹\n",
        "os.makedirs(output_folder, exist_ok=True)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "8aza1-pZRZQJ"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "transform = transforms.Compose([\n",
        "    transforms.Grayscale(num_output_channels=1),  # 转为灰度图\n",
        "    transforms.Resize((28, 28)),                  # 调整为28x28\n",
        "    transforms.ToTensor()                         # 转为张量\n",
        "])"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "x1rOf6ILRcgX"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "device = torch.device(\"cuda\" if torch.cuda.is_available() else \"cpu\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "jWVyUBL0Rc6I"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "file_list = [f for f in os.listdir(input_folder) if f.endswith('.jpg')]"
      ]
    },

      ],
      "source": [
        "for file_name in file_list:\n",
        "    input_path = os.path.join(input_folder, file_name)\n",
        "    image = Image.open(input_path).convert(\"RGB\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    tensor_image = transform(image).to(device)\n",
        "\n",
        "    output_path = os.path.join(output_folder, file_name)\n",
        "    transforms.ToPILImage()(tensor_image.cpu()).save(output_path)\n",
        "\n",
        "    plt.imshow(tensor_image.cpu().squeeze(0), cmap='gray')\n",
        "    plt.title(file_name)\n",
        "    plt.axis('off')\n",
        "    plt.show()"
      ]
    },
